      <h1>Strengthen Your Prefrontal Cortex: The Neuroscience of Self-Control and Discipline</h1>
      <p class="article-subtitle">The prefrontal cortex is your brain's executive center — responsible for self-control, planning, and rational decision-making. Learn how to protect and strengthen it for better performance.</p>
